Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.89,0:00:03.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The seasonal uniform change!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.06,0:00:06.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's been so muggy lately, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.56,0:00:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even just changing into short sleeves\Nfeels much more comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.90,0:00:11.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.00,0:01:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}RESPONSIBILITY AND DUTY
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.00,0:01:49.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Relationship advice?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.54,0:01:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! I don't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.84,0:01:57.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}But I heard that the student council\Ngives advice for that kind of thing, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.55,0:01:58.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KAGUYA WANTS TO HANDLE IT
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.34,0:01:59.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You're the only one I can count on,\NMiss Kaguya!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.39,0:02:01.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.01,0:02:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The president here often says\Nthat lending an ear to the students' troubles
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.06,0:02:08.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,is also a duty of the student council.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.02,0:02:09.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.48,0:02:13.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,what's the trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.73,0:02:17.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know how to break up\Nsmoothly with my boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.99,0:02:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}I thought it would be\Ntwo or three steps before that point!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.62,0:02:27.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Advice about having a boyfriend.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.04,0:02:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You're really popular, and I'm sure\Nyou know a lot about love!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.58,0:02:36.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I've never even gone out with anyone,\Nso how could I possibly answer that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.88,0:02:36.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I knew I could come to you\Nfor a great idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.55,0:02:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Her expectations are too high!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.97,0:02:43.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But Shinomiya gave romantic advice once,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.30,0:02:45.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}so there's no way\NI can tell her it's beyond me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.64,0:02:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll just have to get through it somehow!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.93,0:02:49.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you want to break up?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.69,0:02:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, he suddenly asked me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.61,0:02:54.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Bam!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.27,0:02:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I said, "Okay" on the spur of the moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.15,0:03:00.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but I didn't really know him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.53,0:03:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And I don't really know\Nhow to communicate with him either.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.12,0:03:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, there's more distance\Nbetween us now than before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.79,0:03:08.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I feel guilty about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.58,0:03:12.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so if it's going to be like this, I figured\Nmaybe we're better off just breaking up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.75,0:03:17.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.25,0:03:19.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Until just before,\Nyou were strangers to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.97,0:03:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So I can see where you're coming from.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.47,0:03:25.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't hate him, though, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.93,0:03:31.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not. But I don't know\Nif what I feel for him is love.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.94,0:03:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you start\Nby telling me his good points?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.48,0:03:37.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What I like about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.78,0:03:41.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Everyone has strong points\Nor something that's cute about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.36,0:03:47.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For example, he's honest\Nor he does well academically.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.58,0:03:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he studies hard\Nor he's actually really kind
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.12,0:03:53.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and can't turn his back\Non someone who's in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.04,0:03:57.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he has a menacing look.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.34,0:04:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A menacing look is a drawback.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.63,0:04:04.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No! Being bothered\Nby your own menacing look is cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.64,0:04:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You like boys who have menacing looks?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.35,0:04:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Forget I said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.60,0:04:12.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The only person around you\Nwith a menacing look that I can think of...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.35,0:04:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's the wrong idea.\NNow let's continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.73,0:04:21.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you find one good thing about him\Nand start to appreciate that,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.11,0:04:23.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you'll soon be able to see\Nmany of his good points,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.53,0:04:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and the next thing you know,\Nyou're unable to take your eyes off of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.24,0:04:28.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And if you see him every day...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.95,0:04:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,little by little, you'll fall in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.00,0:04:34.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's what an acquaintance told me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.67,0:04:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not talking about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.75,0:04:37.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.04,0:04:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's really not about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.30,0:04:42.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because there isn't anyone\NI'm in love with!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.72,0:04:44.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But the way you said it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.68,0:04:46.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I overheard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.72,0:04:47.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Fujiwara?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.39,0:04:50.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}It's no fair to have girls' talk without me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.60,0:04:55.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Please leave an issue like that\Nto Love Detective Chika!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.14,0:04:55.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LOVE DETECTIVE CHIKA
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.69,0:04:58.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you breathing hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.77,0:05:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I was here from the beginning,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.19,0:05:04.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but made a mad dash to the drama club\Nto borrow this costume.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.36,0:05:08.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're in a quandary, because you can't\Nfind your feelings for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.87,0:05:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.20,0:05:11.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.37,0:05:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then this great detective will find\Nthat lost property called "love"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.33,0:05:16.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and return it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.75,0:05:22.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, imagine him flirting with another girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.63,0:05:24.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.01,0:05:26.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just try to imagine it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.97,0:05:35.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gloomy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.97,0:05:35.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}GLOOMY...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.43,0:05:36.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Grrr.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.43,0:05:38.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}GRRR GRRR
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.10,0:05:41.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't like that feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.19,0:05:42.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.98,0:05:44.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, that's jealousy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.65,0:05:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't like that image\Nbecause you like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.82,0:05:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The more unpleasant the feeling,\Nthe deeper the love!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.95,0:05:56.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Love?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.25,0:06:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, you also like him, Miss Kashiwagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.08,0:05:58.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}No, there's no way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.33,0:06:02.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I don't feel that way about the president,\Nright? I mean, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.25,0:06:02.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You should take that feeling\Nand nurture it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.09,0:06:04.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.38,0:06:08.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I suspected myself of being a cold person\Nfor not being able to fall in love with someone
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.18,0:06:11.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,who went as far as professing\Nhis love for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.05,0:06:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.85,0:06:16.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you're right! I actually do love him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.81,0:06:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}It's like she was talked into it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.19,0:06:24.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do\Nto talk to him more naturally?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.19,0:06:24.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}I have to give\Nmore appropriate advice, too!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.03,0:06:26.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good question.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.99,0:06:28.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cognitive balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.65,0:06:32.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can probably use\Nthe Romeo and Juliet effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.24,0:06:34.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Romeo and Juliet?\N- Romeo and Juliet?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.70,0:06:37.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Romeo and Juliet's love faced obstacles.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.87,0:06:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The idea is that love deepens
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.04,0:06:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,when a couple shares\Na powerful enemy they face.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.00,0:06:46.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A powerful enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.21,0:06:49.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't have to be a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.13,0:06:51.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A shared imaginary enemy is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.76,0:06:53.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have an enemy like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.76,0:06:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! Everyone has\Na powerful enemy they have to face!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.18,0:06:59.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.23,0:07:01.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.15,0:07:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,this society!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.36,0:07:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Society?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.65,0:07:08.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Unending war! The ever-expanding gap\Nbetween rich and poor!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.36,0:07:10.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There are no enemies\Nmore powerful than that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.36,0:07:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}Wait. It should be something minor\Nlike entrance exams or everyday troubles.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.53,0:07:17.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see! So the two of us\Nshould rebel against this corrupt society!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.37,0:07:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's a large-scale challenge!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.29,0:07:22.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Understood!\NThe two of us will prepare!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.12,0:07:23.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.04,0:07:24.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.38,0:07:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Will it be okay? Did we just create\Ntwo antisocial deviants?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.43,0:07:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.56,0:07:39.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please donate to the fund!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.14,0:07:41.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.94,0:07:45.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please donate to the fund!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.19,0:07:48.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}It seems they were both\Nalready interested in charity work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.69,0:07:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.40,0:07:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}This has become a good opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.24,0:07:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The feeling of wishing for peace...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.11,0:07:57.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That may be the true meaning\Nof rebelling against society.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.54,0:07:58.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.12,0:08:04.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So, her boyfriend is the one\Nwho went to the president for advice.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.13,0:08:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,President?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.76,0:08:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Shinomiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.51,0:08:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.80,0:08:20.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Oh, I applied to do\Noff-campus fundraising activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.93,0:08:25.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Please donate to the fund!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.31,0:08:26.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, when I saw those two who don't seem\Nto be doing it on a whim or as a pastime,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.69,0:08:27.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.31,0:08:29.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,who are inexperienced but eager...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.36,0:08:31.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Please donate to the fund!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.07,0:08:32.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,it made me feel like supporting them\Neven if it's not much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.94,0:08:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.41,0:08:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.41,0:08:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Please donate to the fund!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.70,0:08:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This kind of activity\Nreally isn't up my alley, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.87,0:08:39.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.20,0:08:44.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is one of the things.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.21,0:08:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}RESULTS OF TODAY'S MATCH:
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.54,0:08:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Results of today's match...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.79,0:08:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5}KAGUYA LOSES
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.50,0:08:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kaguya loses.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.25,0:08:51.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PLEASE DONATE TO THE FUND
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.00,0:08:51.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}PLEASE
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.38,0:08:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}MIYUKI SHIROGANE\NWANTS TO SHOW OFF
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.02,0:09:04.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,WHACK
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.52,0:09:12.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was so close!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.15,0:09:13.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not athletic!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.15,0:09:13.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}NOTE: NOT ATHLETIC
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.90,0:09:17.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When it comes to studying,\NShirogane excels,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.16,0:09:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but as for athletics, he's a catastrophe,\Nunfit for any human to see.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.24,0:09:25.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He delivered newspapers for many years,\Nand in the summertime, worked as a mover.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.87,0:09:29.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's easily able to ride his bike\Nthe 15 kilometers to school every day.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.46,0:09:33.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Miyuki Shirogane definitely doesn't suffer\Nfrom a lack of physical ability.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.84,0:09:38.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}He just has an alarming lack\Nof coordination! That's the cause!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.51,0:09:42.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So, in order to protect\Nhis social status at Shuchiin Academy,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.26,0:09:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}daily extraordinary training is essential!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.48,0:09:47.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}We've got volleyball next week.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.94,0:09:51.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}I have to get to the point\Nof average ability by then.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.86,0:09:53.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}At this rate...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.53,0:09:55.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please take this seriously.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.82,0:09:58.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It looks like a dying alpaca,\Nbut is that the president?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.11,0:09:58.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}Really?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.16,0:10:01.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}That dying alpaca?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.08,0:10:04.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How cute.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.20,0:10:07.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.42,0:10:10.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why isn't this working?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.13,0:10:13.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,President, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.42,0:10:14.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, no prob...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.30,0:10:16.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fujiwara!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.22,0:10:18.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.63,0:10:21.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot this here. Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.97,0:10:24.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Did she see me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.10,0:10:28.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's over.\NGood at both sports and studies...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.23,0:10:31.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The well-rounded\NPresident Shirogane brand...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.40,0:10:36.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}Even though I didn't do anything wrong,\Nmy flawless image will...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.94,0:10:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Did I study for the test? Not really.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.61,0:10:40.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is really bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.45,0:10:45.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Playing with a ball is so much fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.00,0:10:46.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, well.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.50,0:10:50.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whatever she thinks about me,\Nit won't do much damage.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.71,0:10:52.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Volleyball is the next sport for P.E., right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.13,0:10:55.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to reserve the gym,\Nso I've been practicing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.21,0:10:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My serve is kind of weak, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.22,0:10:59.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.47,0:11:02.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Want me to teach you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.60,0:11:07.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Look, you can't teach someone\Nunless you can do it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.93,0:11:10.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm okay at volleyball!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.90,0:11:11.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.11,0:11:14.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.19,0:11:16.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.19,0:11:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PRESIDENT'S CRITERIA
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.44,0:11:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}How could her serve be so polished?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.82,0:11:20.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How'd you like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.03,0:11:23.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-I had no idea you possessed\Nsuch a special skill!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.95,0:11:28.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I bet if I taught you,\Nyou'd improve in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.37,0:11:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GRIN GRIN
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.66,0:11:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}President! When you're\Nasking someone for help,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.46,0:11:35.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}what kind of attitude is appropriate?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.96,0:11:40.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please teach me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.22,0:11:42.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sure! No problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.34,0:11:46.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, first let me see\Nexactly what the problem is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.93,0:11:48.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please show me your serve several times.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.10,0:11:50.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.32,0:12:03.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why does that happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.49,0:12:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.20,0:12:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how many times I try,\NI keep hitting myself in the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.49,0:12:11.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And if I'm careful about my head,\Nmy timing is totally off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.25,0:12:14.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm perfectly deadlocked!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.33,0:12:16.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.67,0:12:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,First of all, when you hit the ball,\Nkeep your eyes open!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.80,0:12:21.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to state the obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.88,0:12:23.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.88,0:12:26.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then open your eyes wide\Nand try to hit the ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.22,0:12:29.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As if that would make a difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.94,0:12:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,See? That didn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.40,0:12:38.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your eyes aren't open!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.07,0:12:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're not open!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.40,0:12:43.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How can you project the feeling,\N"I did what you said, but it didn't work"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.53,0:12:46.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Look! They weren't even open\None millimeter!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.37,0:12:48.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.83,0:12:51.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I have what they call "the yips"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.41,0:12:52.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What arrogance!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.79,0:12:57.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,President, maybe your image of yourself\Nisn't in sync with your actual movements!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.59,0:13:00.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start with jumping\Nwith your eyes open!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.92,0:13:03.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to be merciless with you,\Nso be prepared!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.59,0:13:04.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.80,0:13:06.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}OGRE
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.05,0:13:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And so...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.89,0:13:09.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1, 2,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.14,0:13:11.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3, 4 ,5...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.93,0:13:15.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,556, 557, 558, 559...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.06,0:13:18.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}984, 985, 986 ,987...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.64,0:13:18.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}No closed eyes when you jump.\NThe ball is your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.15,0:13:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}And so, with morning and evening\Ntraining sessions, three days passed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.99,0:13:26.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,President...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.53,0:13:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe this is enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.45,0:13:32.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think you're good enough to be\Nat the level of a person who just sucks at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.37,0:13:36.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Compared to when you were a creature,\Nyou've made a lot of progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.75,0:13:37.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.58,0:13:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can still...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.29,0:13:41.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,do more!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.55,0:13:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you working so hard for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.13,0:13:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't want them\Nto see me look like a dork.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.14,0:13:50.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If they're going to see me,\NI want them to see me look cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.64,0:13:59.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you talking\Nabout the person you like, President?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.40,0:14:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all!\NYou've got romance on the brain!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.86,0:14:05.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to hide it from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.03,0:14:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who's she? Who's she?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.99,0:14:06.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.74,0:14:08.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.24,0:14:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't pester me about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.87,0:14:20.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.46,0:14:22.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You did it! You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.59,0:14:24.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Fujiwara. Thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.26,0:14:29.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was so tough!\NBut you persevered until you achieved it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.89,0:14:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Fujiwara.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.30,0:14:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next teach me how to toss and receive!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.65,0:14:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ONE WEEK LATER
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.74,0:14:49.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.03,0:14:50.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shirogane!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.79,0:14:59.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Fujiwara?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.46,0:15:03.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I raised that boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.71,0:15:04.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're his mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.96,0:15:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}RESULTS OF TODAY'S MATCH:
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.09,0:15:06.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Results of today's match...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.71,0:15:09.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shirogane and Fujiwara's victory!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.71,0:15:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5}SHIROGANE AND\NFUJIWARA'S VICTORY
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.97,0:15:12.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,YES, WELL...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.72,0:15:13.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'LL NEVER DO IT AGAIN.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.47,0:15:21.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KAGUYA WANTS TO BE COVERED
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.81,0:15:21.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}All right. Ishigami finished dealing\Nwith the aftermath of that last mixer...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.90,0:15:24.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so there really isn't anything\Nfor us to do today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.77,0:15:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we take the day off?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.90,0:15:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sure! Then you'd better call\Nfor an early pickup, Miss Kaguya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.36,0:15:30.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.41,0:15:35.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,the car has a flat or something,\Nso I thought I'd walk home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.20,0:15:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be kidnapped?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.37,0:15:41.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Not much evidence is left on a rainy day,\Nso that's when they target you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.21,0:15:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Please don't say things\Nthat'll make me nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.63,0:15:48.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to give you a lift,\Nbut I have somewhere to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.71,0:15:51.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}Shinomiya is going to walk home?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.26,0:15:51.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay.\NI appreciate the sentiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.47,0:15:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}Then maybe that'll work?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.43,0:15:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The turning point of the season.\NThe rainy season.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.31,0:15:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sharing an umbrella!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.10,0:16:00.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Two shoulders close together\Nunder one umbrella,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.94,0:16:03.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}an event that immediately closes\Nthe distance between man and woman.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.94,0:16:07.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The rainy season is the ideal season\Nto share an umbrella.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.69,0:16:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What nonsense.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.44,0:16:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shamefully jostling each other\Nunder one umbrella...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.70,0:16:17.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I do recognize the meaning\Nbehind sharing an umbrella.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.99,0:16:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In the realm of romance,\Nwhat should be feared the most{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.33,0:16:22.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}is summer vacation magic.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.46,0:16:24.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Spending summer vacation\Nwith your sweetheart."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.83,0:16:26.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That brand is so sought after{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.71,0:16:29.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}that before summer vacation starts,\Nevaluation of the opposite sex{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.17,0:16:31.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}takes place everywhere\Nthroughout the school.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.39,0:16:40.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sharing an umbrella emphasizes to onlookers\Nan intimacy with a member of the opposite sex,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.18,0:16:41.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5}DAMN
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.18,0:16:42.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5}MARKING COMPLETE!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.18,0:16:43.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5}HE'S TAKEN
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.56,0:16:43.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and is the most efficient way\Nto mark someone as being excluded{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.98,0:16:46.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}from the group\Nof "summer sweetheart candidates."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.94,0:16:50.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's really coming down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.48,0:16:53.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It wasn't raining at all this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.36,0:16:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's pretty much one way\Nthat sharing an umbrella works.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.20,0:17:00.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}One... "A" has forgotten to bring\Nan umbrella and is just standing there.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.87,0:17:04.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Two... Unable to ignore that,\N"B" asks, "Wanna share?"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.20,0:17:05.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5}WANNA SHARE?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.46,0:17:05.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SUCCESS!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.88,0:17:07.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Well, should we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.17,0:17:08.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In short, the success\Nof sharing an umbrella...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.59,0:17:08.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.54,0:17:10.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}depends on the "I forgot my umbrella" appeal!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.38,0:17:12.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.26,0:17:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?\NI don't have an umbrella.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.26,0:17:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Shoot, I forgot my umbrella.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.59,0:17:16.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}COMPETITION BATTING!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.80,0:17:16.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Batting!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.51,0:17:22.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}An umbrella sharing event begins\Nwith one person forgetting their umbrella.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.14,0:17:26.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But if they both forget their umbrellas,\Nthere are no developments!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.73,0:17:29.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's just two people\Nwho have forgotten to bring an umbrella!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.86,0:17:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You forgot your umbrella, too, Shinomiya?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.82,0:17:36.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It just slipped my mind,\Nsince I usually get picked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.95,0:17:38.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.32,0:17:40.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I didn't check the weather forecast.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.66,0:17:43.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think\Nwe were in for a storm like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.83,0:17:48.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}Of course, it's all a bluff!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.38,0:17:52.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}They both have folding umbrellas\Nin their bags!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.63,0:17:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What do I do?\NTell her I have an umbrella now?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.30,0:17:58.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But if I do that...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.18,0:18:00.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, my.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.47,0:18:04.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You wanted to get under my umbrella\Nso badly that you lied about your umbrella?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.43,0:18:06.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Good grief.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.14,0:18:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How cute.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.69,0:18:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.44,0:18:13.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Already, taking out the umbrella\Nwould expose a meaningful lie.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.53,0:18:17.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And that would also directly link to inviting\Nthe other person to share the umbrella.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.32,0:18:19.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That would clearly spell defeat.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.99,0:18:22.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}Wait. If she doesn't have a ride,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.74,0:18:26.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}I'm sure someone from the Shinomiya house\Nwould've given her an umbrella.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.25,0:18:28.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}It wouldn't matter\Nthat it slipped her mind!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.62,0:18:30.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}I've got your number, President.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.38,0:18:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}You have an umbrella\Nin that bag, don't you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.30,0:18:36.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}You're lying because you're too embarrassed\Nto invite me under your umbrella.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.92,0:18:38.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In this situation,\Nthe condition for victory...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.93,0:18:42.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}is none other than exposing\Nthe other person's lie!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.89,0:18:46.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Shinomiya,\Nmaybe you've actually got one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.85,0:18:48.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shirogane made the first move.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.98,0:18:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your usual ride had a flat today,\Non the day it rains.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.94,0:18:56.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But today of all days, someone like you,\Nwho always plans ahead, forgot her umbrella.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.28,0:19:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}How likely is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.08,0:19:04.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.87,0:19:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.41,0:19:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not enough information.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.25,0:19:10.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Should I gamble on a game-winning hit?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.17,0:19:12.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}If we're talking planning ahead,\Nyou do the same, President.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.21,0:19:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.54,0:19:19.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Before, you said you didn't check\Nthe weather forecast, but I find that odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.51,0:19:21.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's odd about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.26,0:19:22.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have days like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.35,0:19:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You always ride your bicycle\Nto school, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.31,0:19:28.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.23,0:19:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Then,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.44,0:19:33.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}why did you take the train today?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.57,0:19:39.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I noticed your bike\Nwasn't in the bike rack today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.74,0:19:40.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}What?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.07,0:19:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I mean, if you think about it,\Nthere's nothing unnatural at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.37,0:19:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}On a rainy day,\Nyou take the train to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.20,0:19:50.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's the reasonable thing to do, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.58,0:19:51.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Say, President...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.79,0:19:55.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you said you missed\Nthe weather forecast, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.63,0:19:59.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then why did you choose\Nto take the train today, of all days?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.55,0:20:01.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.72,0:20:05.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you saw it, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.80,0:20:06.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The weather forecast.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.93,0:20:10.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The difference in preparation!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.98,0:20:15.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you just thought\Nyou forgot to bring an umbrella.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.15,0:20:19.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,President, would you take a look\Nin your bag to see if it's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.78,0:20:22.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The difference in advance preparation\Nwill decide the outcome of the game!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.24,0:20:27.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It didn't even take Shirogane an hour\Nto devise his umbrella-sharing plan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.95,0:20:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}On the other hand,\NKaguya confirmed the weather report.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.54,0:20:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}She carefully looked at the weather map,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.29,0:20:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}used an awl to pierce\Nthe tire of her ride,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.04,0:20:36.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and checked the bicycle rack.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.63,0:20:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The amount of advance preparation\Ngave her a big lead.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.46,0:20:41.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}Naturally, she predicted\Nthis situation, as well.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.01,0:20:44.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}Now I'll score a point for good measure!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.30,0:20:48.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll just get soaked\Nwalking home in the rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.93,0:20:52.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}GRIN
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.93,0:20:53.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Kaguya, you forgot your umbrella?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.56,0:20:59.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a spare in the classroom,\Nso please use this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.61,0:21:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please be more careful for next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.32,0:21:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Absent-minded Miss Kaguya!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.57,0:21:07.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, see ya tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.87,0:21:15.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I had him! I was one step away!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.88,0:21:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why does that girl always spoil it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.79,0:21:20.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now that it's come to this...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.13,0:21:24.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.38,0:21:27.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm giving you this umbrella, President!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.26,0:21:29.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do what you want with it! Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.01,0:21:32.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, that umbrella belongs to Fujiwara.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.06,0:21:33.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm subletting it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.43,0:21:34.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, look...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.32,0:21:42.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.36,0:21:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How about I borrow half of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.04,0:22:00.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose that will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.81,0:22:15.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Results of today's match...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.48,0:22:20.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}RESULTS OF TODAY'S MATCH:
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.98,0:22:19.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A tie.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.98,0:22:20.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5}A TIE
